videos.description: Holton Hill grabs the tipped ball off of a Maryland receiver's hand and runs it back 31 yards to give Texas an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas' Hill intercepts Maryland for pick-six) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Hill intercepts Maryland for pick-six

videos.description: Maryland's Tyrrelle Pigrome fakes the handoff and books it 25 yards to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Terps QB Pigrome takes it to the house) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Terps QB Pigrome takes it to the house

videos.description: Terps QB Tyrrell Pigrome makes a beautiful throw to WR D.J. Moore to break the 7-7 tie with Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Maryland's Moore snags TD in end zone) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's Moore snags TD in end zone

videos.description: Texas' 44-yard field goal attempt is blocked by Maryland's Joshua Rowland and taken back by Antoine Brooks for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Terps return Texas' blocked FG attempt for TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Terps return Texas' blocked FG attempt for TD

videos.description: QB Tyrell Pigrome sails it to WR Taivon Jacobs for a 46-yard TD pass to put Maryland up 27-7.
videos.headline: Terps' Jacobs catches Pigrome's pass for TD

videos.description: Terrapins kicker Adam Greene banks his 26-yard field goal attempt to cushion Maryland's 30-14 lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Maryland's Greene 26-yard FG is good

videos.description: Texas busts through Maryland's line to block the field goal attempt, and Holton Hill picks up the loose ball for a 65-yard touchdown return.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hill takes blocked field goal for Texas TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hill takes blocked field goal for Texas TD

videos.description: QB Shane Buechele finds Armanti Foreman over the middle for a 33-yard TD to cut in the Maryland lead.
videos.headline: Texas' Buechele connects with Foreman for TD

videos.description: Ty Johnson goes up the middle to score for Maryland, making the score 36-27.
videos.headline: Terps' Johnson answers Texas with TD run

videos.description: Texas QB Shane Buechele rushes the end zone and dives for the 3-yard touchdown in the third quarter to cut Maryland's lead to 37-34.
videos.headline: QB Buechele hustles to the end zone

videos.description: On an extra point attempt in the third quarter, Maryland receives a five-yard penalty for "failure to wear proper equipment" because they had two players wearing number 57 on the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Maryland gets interesting five-yard penalty) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland gets interesting five-yard penalty

videos.description: Maryland freshman QB Kasim Hill runs 3 yards to the goal line to cushion the lead over Texas 44-32 in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Terps extend lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Maryland's Jake Funk cuts up the field in the fourth quarter for the 12-yard touchdown to extend the lead to 51-34 over the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Terps' Funk gets to the goal
